text: Priozerny () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Aksaraysky Selsoviet, Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 18 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 63 km from Astrakhan, 34 km from Krasny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Priozerny, Astrakhan Oblast
